_sText: Hey, I created this a while ago, and finally decided to upload it to fpsbanana.com. Well this map is based in a city environment in a random business. Also this is a beta map, even though there are not any bugs that have been brought to my attention. The main things that are lacking are models and whatnot, and the skybox probably needs to be raised. But other that that is a awesome map in my opinion.
